## ğŸ”¹ Challenge 6 â€” Merge Conflict

```bash
git switch -c conflict-branch
echo 'puts "Conflict from branch"' > greet.rb
git commit -am "Branch conflict"

git switch main
echo 'puts "Conflict from main"' > greet.rb
git commit -am "Main conflict"

git merge conflict-branch
```

Fix conflict manually â†’ then:

```bash
git add greet.rb
git commit
```

