## ğŸ”¹ Challenge 9 â€” GitHub PR Workflow â­

### Push to GitHub

```bash
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOURNAME/git-mastery-lab.git
git push -u origin main
```

### Fork â†’ Feature â†’ PR

```bash
git switch -c pr-feature
echo "PR practice" >> README.md
git commit -am "Practice PR"
git push origin pr-feature
```

â¡ Open PR on GitHub
â¡ Review â†’ merge â†’ delete branch

Cleanup:

```bash
git branch -d pr-feature
```

