## ğŸ”¹ Challenge 10 â€” Advanced

### Rebase

```bash
git switch -c rebase-branch
echo "Line 1" >> README.md
git commit -am "Commit 1"
echo "Line 2" >> README.md
git commit -am "Commit 2"

git switch main
git rebase rebase-branch
```

